Class LocListener

All Implemented Interfaces:
LocationListener
public class LocListener
extends Object
implements LocationListener

The listener interface for receiving location events. The class that is interested in processing a location event implements this interface, and the object created with that class is registered with a component using the component's addLocListener method. When the location event occurs, that object's appropriate method is invoked. LocEvent
